* Keyboard Shortcuts System Implementation Plan

** Project Overview
   This document outlines the complete implementation plan for a customizable keyboard shortcut system
   in the Mindscape application. The system will allow users to navigate, select, and perform actions
   using configurable keyboard combinations.

** Goals and Requirements
*** Primary Goals
    - ( ) Enable keyboard-only navigation throughout the application
    - ( ) Provide customizable key mappings for all major actions
    - ( ) Support multiple default keymap profiles (Vim, Emacs, Arrow keys)
    - ( ) Persist user customizations to S3 storage
    - ( ) Provide intuitive keymap editor interface

*** Technical Requirements
    - ( ) Frontend keyboard event management system
    - ( ) Backend API for keymap CRUD operations
    - ( ) S3 integration for keymap persistence
    - ( ) Context-aware action filtering
    - ( ) Conflict detection and resolution
    - ( ) Cross-browser compatibility

** Architecture Design

*** Frontend Architecture
**** Core Components
     @code typescript
     // Keyboard Manager - Central event handling
     class KeyboardManager {
       private mappings: Map<string, KeyMapping>;
       private listeners: Map<string, Function[]>;
       private currentContext: string[];
     }

     // Action Registry - Available keyboard actions
     interface KeyboardAction {
       id: string;
       name: string;
       description: string;
       category: 'navigation' | 'selection' | 'creation' | 'global';
       defaultKeys: string[];
       context?: string[];
     }

     // Keymap Schema - User configurations
     interface KeymapSchema {
       id: string;
       name: string;
       description: string;
       version: string;
       userId: string;
       mappings: KeyMapping[];
       createdAt: string;
       updatedAt: string;
     }
     @end

**** File Structure
     ```
     web/src/keyboard/
     ├── KeyboardManager.ts     # Core event handling
     ├── actions.ts             # Action definitions
     ├── keymaps.ts            # Default keymap profiles
     ├── useKeyboard.ts        # React/Solid hooks
     ├── types.ts              # TypeScript interfaces
     └── utils.ts              # Helper functions

     web/src/contexts/
     └── KeyboardContext.tsx   # Global state management

     web/src/components/KeymapEditor/
     ├── KeymapEditor.tsx      # Main editor component
     ├── ActionList.tsx        # Available actions list
     ├── KeyCapture.tsx        # Key combination capture
     ├── KeymapPreview.tsx     # Current mappings preview
     └── KeymapImportExport.tsx # Import/export functionality
     ```

*** Backend Architecture
**** Database Schema
     @code sql
     CREATE TABLE user_keymaps (
         id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
         user_id UUID REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
         name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
         description TEXT,
         keymap_data JSONB NOT NULL,
         is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
         created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW(),
         updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
     );

     CREATE INDEX idx_user_keymaps_user_id ON user_keymaps(user_id);
     CREATE INDEX idx_user_keymaps_active ON user_keymaps(user_id, is_active);
     @end

**** API Endpoints
     ```
     GET    /api/keymaps              # Get user's keymaps
     POST   /api/keymaps              # Create new keymap
     PUT    /api/keymaps/:id          # Update keymap
     DELETE /api/keymaps/:id          # Delete keymap
     POST   /api/keymaps/:id/activate # Set as active keymap
     GET    /api/keymaps/defaults     # Get default keymaps
     POST   /api/keymaps/import       # Import keymap from file
     GET    /api/keymaps/:id/export   # Export keymap to file
     ```

**** S3 Storage Structure
     ```
     mindscape-keymaps/
     ├── users/
     │   └── {userId}/
     │       ├── keymaps/
     │       │   ├── {keymapId}.json
     │       │   └── backup_{timestamp}.json
     │       └── metadata.json
     └── defaults/
         ├── vim.json
         ├── emacs.json
         └── arrows.json
     ```

** Implementation Phases

*** Phase 1: Core Infrastructure (Week 1)
**** Backend Development
     - ( ) Create database migration for keymap storage
     - ( ) Implement basic CRUD API endpoints
     - ( ) Add S3 integration for keymap persistence
     - ( ) Create keymap service layer
     - ( ) Add API tests

**** Frontend Core Module
     - ( ) Implement KeyboardManager class
     - ( ) Define default action registry
     - ( ) Create basic event handling system
     - ( ) Add TypeScript interfaces
     - ( ) Implement keyboard context provider

*** Phase 2: Integration & Context (Week 2)
**** Component Integration
     - ( ) Add keyboard hooks to Home component
     - ( ) Integrate with Folder navigation
     - ( ) Add bookmark navigation shortcuts
     - ( ) Implement context-aware filtering
     - ( ) Add global navigation shortcuts

**** Default Keymaps
     - ( ) Create Vim-style keymap profile
     - ( ) Create Emacs-style keymap profile
     - ( ) Create Arrow key navigation profile
     - ( ) Add accessibility-focused profile
     - ( ) Test cross-browser compatibility

*** Phase 3: Editor UI (Week 3)
**** Keymap Editor Development
     - ( ) Create main editor interface
     - ( ) Implement key combination capture
     - ( ) Add action categorization and filtering
     - ( ) Create conflict detection system
     - ( ) Add visual feedback for key bindings

**** Settings Integration
     - ( ) Add keyboard settings page
     - ( ) Implement keymap switching interface
     - ( ) Create import/export functionality
     - ( ) Add reset to defaults option
     - ( ) Integrate with user profile

*** Phase 4: Polish & Testing (Week 4)
**** Advanced Features
     - ( ) Multi-key sequence support
     - ( ) Context help and tooltips
     - ( ) Keymap sharing between users
     - ( ) Performance optimization
     - ( ) Mobile device considerations

**** Testing & Quality Assurance
     - ( ) Cross-browser testing
     - ( ) Accessibility testing
     - ( ) Performance benchmarking
     - ( ) User experience testing
     - ( ) Documentation creation

** Default Action Definitions

*** Navigation Actions
    | Action ID | Description | Default Keys | Context |
	|---|---|---|---|
    | navigate_up | Move selection up | ArrowUp, k | folder-view, bookmark-list |
    | navigate_down | Move selection down | ArrowDown, j | folder-view, bookmark-list |
    | navigate_left | Navigate to parent | ArrowLeft, h | folder-view |
    | navigate_right | Navigate to child | ArrowRight, l | folder-view |
    | navigate_first | Jump to first item | Home, gg | folder-view, bookmark-list |
    | navigate_last | Jump to last item | End, G | folder-view, bookmark-list |

*** Selection Actions
    | Action ID | Description | Default Keys | Context |
	|---|---|---|---|
    | select_item | Select current item | Space | folder-view, bookmark-list |
    | select_all | Select all items | Ctrl+a | folder-view, bookmark-list |
    | clear_selection | Clear all selections | Escape | folder-view, bookmark-list |
    | toggle_selection | Toggle item selection | Ctrl+Space | folder-view, bookmark-list |

*** Creation Actions
    | Action ID | Description | Default Keys | Context |
	|---|---|---|---|
    | create_folder | Create new folder | Ctrl+Shift+n | folder-view |
    | create_bookmark | Create new bookmark | Ctrl+n | folder-view |
    | duplicate_item | Duplicate selected item | Ctrl+d | folder-view, bookmark-list |

*** Global Actions
    | Action ID | Description | Default Keys | Context |
	|---|---|---|---|
    | focus_search | Focus search bar | /, Ctrl+f | global |
    | toggle_keymap_help | Show/hide help | ? | global |
    | save_current_state | Save current state | Ctrl+s | global |
    | open_settings | Open settings | Ctrl+, | global |

** Default Keymap Profiles

*** Vim-Style Navigation
    @code json
    {
      "name": "Vim Navigation",
      "description": "Vi/Vim inspired keyboard navigation",
      "mappings": [
        { "actionId": "navigate_up", "keys": ["k"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "navigate_down", "keys": ["j"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "navigate_left", "keys": ["h"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "navigate_right", "keys": ["l"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "navigate_first", "keys": ["g", "g"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "navigate_last", "keys": ["G"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "select_item", "keys": ["Enter"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "create_folder", "keys": ["o"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "create_bookmark", "keys": ["i"], "enabled": true },
        { "actionId": "focus_search", "keys": ["/"], "enabled": true }
      ]
    }
    @end

