** JSON Schema Specification

*** Keymap Schema
    @code json
    {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "title": "Mindscape Keymap Schema",
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Unique identifier for the keymap"
        },
        "name": {
          "type": "string",
          "maxLength": 100,
          "description": "Human-readable name for the keymap"
        },
        "description": {
          "type": "string",
          "maxLength": 500,
          "description": "Description of the keymap"
        },
        "version": {
          "type": "string",
          "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$",
          "description": "Semantic version of the keymap"
        },
        "userId": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "ID of the user who owns this keymap"
        },
        "isDefault": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "description": "Whether this is a system default keymap"
        },
        "mappings": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "actionId": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "ID of the action to trigger"
              },
              "keys": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": { "type": "string" },
                "minItems": 1,
                "description": "Key combination to trigger the action"
              },
              "enabled": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "description": "Whether this mapping is active"
              },
              "context": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": { "type": "string" },
                "description": "Contexts where this mapping applies"
              }
            },
            "required": ["actionId", "keys", "enabled"]
          }
        },
        "metadata": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "createdAt": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
            "updatedAt": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
            "lastUsed": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
            "useCount": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 }
          }
        }
      },
      "required": ["id", "name", "version", "userId", "mappings"]
    }
    @end

** Implementation Checklist

*** Backend Tasks
    - ( ) Database migration for keymap storage
    - ( ) API endpoints for CRUD operations
    - ( ) S3 service integration
    - ( ) Keymap validation middleware
