** Future Enhancements

*** Advanced Features
    - ( ) Keymap sharing between users
    - ( ) Community keymap repository
    - ( ) Macro recording and playback
    - ( ) Context-sensitive help system
    - ( ) Analytics for popular key combinations
    - ( ) Mobile device support
